{"title":"Limited edition 2022 Bianchi Specialissima Giro105 celebrates 105th Giro d’Italia in sunset pink","link":"https://bikerumor.com/limited-edition-2022-bianchi-specialissima-giro105-celebrates-105th-giro-ditalia-in-sunset-pink/","date":1636722595000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12080008/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_Dolomites.jpg\" data-fancybox=\"\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12080008/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_Dolomites-800x533.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Bianchi Specialissima Giro105 limited edition 105th anniversary Giro dItalia lightweight carbon road racing bike, photo by Tornanti.cc, riding the Dolomites\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12080008/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_Dolomites-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12080008/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_Dolomites-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12080008/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_Dolomites-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12080008/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_Dolomites-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12080008/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_Dolomites-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12080008/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_Dolomites.jpg 2000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></a><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-278263\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>Bianchi’s 750g superlight carbon Specialissima road bike is getting a special Giro105 limited edition, celebrating the upcoming 105th edition of the Italian Grand Tour in a subtle white and pink look inspired by sunsets in the Dolomites. Just 105 of the lightweight disc brake climber’s bikes will be made available ahead of the 2022 Giro d’Italia so you might snatch one up quick if you want to build up a unique Italian superbike.</p><h2>2022 Bianchi Specialissima Giro105 ltd. ed. road bike</h2><p>Updated even lighter just last fall in its move to disc brakes, Bianchi’s <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/10/26/2021-bianchi-specialissima-cv-goes-lightweight-in-modern-disc-brake-road-race-update/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">new Specialissima</a> packs their NASA-developed vibration-damping <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2013/04/05/bianchis-new-infinito-cv-borrows-from-nasa-introduces-countervail-for-cycling/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Countervail</a> tech into a lightweight climber’s bike with pro race level stiffness and precision handling -what they call their most versatile all-rounder road racing bike.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075958/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_frameset-black.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075958/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_frameset-black.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Bianchi Specialissima Giro105 limited edition 105th anniversary Giro dItalia lightweight carbon road racing bike, frameset\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075958/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_frameset-black.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075958/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_frameset-black-297x167.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075958/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_frameset-black-800x450.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075958/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_frameset-black-120x68.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075958/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_frameset-black-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075958/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_frameset-black-1536x864.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p>Now, to honor more than a century of Giro d’Italia racing, the Specialissima gets a limited Giro105 edition with a paint job to reflect the “great beauty” of Italy. 105 bikes for 105 years of the Giro, each frameset will be handpainted in Italy and individually numbered 001-150 on the toptube.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075951/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_numbered.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075951/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_numbered.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Bianchi Specialissima Giro105 limited edition 105th anniversary Giro dItalia lightweight carbon road racing bike, individually numbered frame\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075951/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_numbered.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075951/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_numbered-297x167.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075951/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_numbered-800x450.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075951/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_numbered-120x68.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075951/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_numbered-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075951/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_numbered-1536x864.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>The paint job feels pleasantly subdued when we think of other Giro pink special editions. Bianchi started with a neutral Bianco Corsa white representing the color of the finish line and rider’s names scrawled on the iconic Alpine climbs in chalk.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075954/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_riding-detail.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075954/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_riding-detail.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Bianchi Specialissima Giro105 limited edition 105th anniversary Giro dItalia lightweight carbon road racing bike, photo by Tornanti.cc,&nbsp;pink frame detail\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075954/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_riding-detail.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075954/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_riding-detail-297x178.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075954/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_riding-detail-800x480.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075954/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_riding-detail-120x72.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075954/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_riding-detail-768x461.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075954/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_riding-detail-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p>Then, the natural Enrosadira pink comes inspired by the color of the skies in the Dolomites at dawn or dusk, with the bike’s paint also changing from gold to pink as perspectives and the light around you shift.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075948/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_fork-detail.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075948/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_fork-detail.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Bianchi Specialissima Giro105 limited edition 105th anniversary Giro dItalia lightweight carbon road racing bike, photo by Tornanti.cc,&nbsp;fork details\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075948/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_fork-detail.jpg 1500w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075948/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_fork-detail-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075948/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_fork-detail-800x533.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075948/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_fork-detail-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075948/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_fork-detail-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\"></a></p><p>Lastly, the fork legs get a ribbon design based on the <em>Trofeo senza Fine</em> (Endless Trophy) awarded to the Giro champion.</p><h3>Tech details</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075944/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_details.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075944/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_details.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Bianchi Specialissima Giro105 limited edition 105th anniversary Giro dItalia lightweight carbon road racing bike, details\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075944/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_details.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075944/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_details-297x178.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075944/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_details-800x480.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075944/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_details-120x72.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075944/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_details-768x461.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075944/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_details-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p>Designed to be pro-level “ultralight and superbly stiff”, the full carbon frame &amp; fork are engineered by Bianchi in Italy, manufactured in Taiwan with CV tech inside, then painted in Italy for a claimed frame weight of 750g, fork weight of 370g fork in a wide seven size range (47-61cm).</p><p><a href=\"http://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2021-Bianchi-Specialissima-CV-lightweight-road-bike_Countervail-light-stiff-carbon-disc-brake-road-race-bike_geometry.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2021-Bianchi-Specialissima-CV-lightweight-road-bike_Countervail-light-stiff-carbon-disc-brake-road-race-bike_geometry-800x640.jpg\" alt=\"2021 Bianchi Specialissima CV lightweight road bike, Countervail light stiff carbon disc brake road race bike,&nbsp;geometry\" width=\"800\" height=\"640\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2021-Bianchi-Specialissima-CV-lightweight-road-bike_Countervail-light-stiff-carbon-disc-brake-road-race-bike_geometry-800x640.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2021-Bianchi-Specialissima-CV-lightweight-road-bike_Countervail-light-stiff-carbon-disc-brake-road-race-bike_geometry-297x238.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2021-Bianchi-Specialissima-CV-lightweight-road-bike_Countervail-light-stiff-carbon-disc-brake-road-race-bike_geometry-120x96.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2021-Bianchi-Specialissima-CV-lightweight-road-bike_Countervail-light-stiff-carbon-disc-brake-road-race-bike_geometry-768x614.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2021-Bianchi-Specialissima-CV-lightweight-road-bike_Countervail-light-stiff-carbon-disc-brake-road-race-bike_geometry-1536x1229.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2021-Bianchi-Specialissima-CV-lightweight-road-bike_Countervail-light-stiff-carbon-disc-brake-road-race-bike_geometry-696x557.jpg 696w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2021-Bianchi-Specialissima-CV-lightweight-road-bike_Countervail-light-stiff-carbon-disc-brake-road-race-bike_geometry-1068x854.jpg 1068w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2021-Bianchi-Specialissima-CV-lightweight-road-bike_Countervail-light-stiff-carbon-disc-brake-road-race-bike_geometry-1920x1536.jpg 1920w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2021-Bianchi-Specialissima-CV-lightweight-road-bike_Countervail-light-stiff-carbon-disc-brake-road-race-bike_geometry-525x420.jpg 525w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2021-Bianchi-Specialissima-CV-lightweight-road-bike_Countervail-light-stiff-carbon-disc-brake-road-race-bike_geometry.jpg 2000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></a></p><p>The limited-edition Bianco Corsa / Enrosadira (<em>that’s Italian for Race White / Alpenglow</em>) frameset features a 1.5” steerer with full 1.5” FSA ACR headset for complete internal routing including the front brake through the steerer, a comfy 27.2mm seatpost with hidden clamp, BB86 PressFit bottom bracket, flat mount disc brakes, 12mm thru-axles, and is compatible with mechanical &amp; electronic drivetrains.</p><h3>Bianchi Specialissima Giro105 – Pricing &amp; availability</h3><div id=\"attachment_278274\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075940/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_frameset.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-278274\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075940/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_frameset.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Bianchi Specialissima Giro105 limited edition 105th anniversary Giro dItalia lightweight carbon road racing bike, frameset\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075940/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_frameset.jpg 2000w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075940/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_frameset-297x178.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075940/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_frameset-800x480.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075940/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_frameset-120x72.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075940/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_frameset-768x461.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075940/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_frameset-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-278274\">2022 Bianchi Specialissima Giro105 limited edition frameset</p></div><p>Only 105 pieces of the limited edition Bianchi Specialissima Giro105 road bike will be made, and only sold as a frameset for 5400€ officially through Bianchi’s website.</p><p>But you should get in touch with your local Bianchi dealer now too, as they are planning to work with buyers to build up complete bikes. And as we all know, if you are trying to get a new Dura-Ace Di2 12-speed groupset in the near future like in these photos, you need to start hunting it now!</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075937/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_complete.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075937/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_complete.jpg\" alt=\"2022 Bianchi Specialissima Giro105 limited edition 105th anniversary Giro dItalia lightweight carbon road racing bike, photo by Tornanti.cc,&nbsp;complete build\" width=\"1500\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075937/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_complete.jpg 1500w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075937/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_complete-297x178.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075937/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_complete-800x480.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075937/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_complete-120x72.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/12075937/2022-Bianchi-Specialissima-Giro105-limited-edition-105th-anniversary-Giro-dItalia-lightweight-carbon-road-racing-bike_photo-by-Tornanti_complete-768x461.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\"></a></p><p>To secure a frameset, you can register interest online now. But they won’t officially go on sale until April 15, 2022… three weeks before the 105th Giro d’Italia kicks off finally with its rescheduled start in Budapest, Hungary after having stayed almost exclusively in Italy the last two years because of COVID-19 concerns.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.bianchi.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>Bianchi.com</em></a></p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"a2a64210025396895a76fc4442702388eba7c56e68d7a2f24ed25ce517b44add","category":"Cycling"}